  "id": "api/core/testing/fakeAsync",
  "title": "fakeAsync",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/testing/src/fake_async.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L26-L52\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/testing/src/fake_async.ts#L26-L52\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/testing\", \"name\": \"@angular/core/testing\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/testing/fakeAsync\", \"name\": \"fakeAsync\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core/testing\">@angular/core/testing</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"fakeasync\">fakeAsync<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync#fakeasync\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label experimental\">试验性的</label>\n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Wraps a function to be executed in the fakeAsync zone:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>microtasks are manually executed by calling <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/flushMicrotasks\" class=\"code-anchor\">flushMicrotasks</a>()</code>,</li>\n<li>timers are synchronous, <code><a href=\"api/core/ApplicationRef#tick\" class=\"code-anchor\">tick()</a></code> simulates the asynchronous passage of time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <a href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync\" class=\"code-anchor\">fakeAsync</a>(fn: Function): (...args: any[]) => any</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>fn</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>Function</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               <p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>(...args: any[]) => any</code>: The function wrapped to be executed in the fakeAsync zone</p>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">If there are any pending timers at the end of the function, an exception will be thrown.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Can be used to wrap inject() calls.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example>\ndescribe('this test', () => {\n  it('looks <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a> but is synchronous', &#x3C;any><a href=\"api/core/testing/fakeAsync\" class=\"code-anchor\">fakeAsync</a>((): void => {\n       let flag = false;\n       setTimeout(() => { flag = true; }, 100);\n       expect(flag).toBe(false);\n       <a href=\"api/core/testing/tick\" class=\"code-anchor\">tick</a>(50);\n       expect(flag).toBe(false);\n       <a href=\"api/core/testing/tick\" class=\"code-anchor\">tick</a>(50);\n       expect(flag).toBe(true);\n     }));\n});\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/tick\n - api/http/testing/MockBackend\n - guide/reactive-forms\n - guide/testing\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/ApplicationRef#tick\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/async\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync#description\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync#example\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync#fakeasync\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync#usage-notes\n - api/core/testing/flushMicrotasks\n - api/core/testing/tick\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/testing/src/fake_async.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L26-L52\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/testing/src/fake_async.ts#L26-L52\n-->"
